[/asy] If $AC = BC$ and $\angle OAC = 18^\circ,$ then how many degrees are in $\angle AOB$? The final Answer is 72^\circ
 ### Proof
 First, let us draw $CO$: [asy] pair pA, pB, pC, pO; pO = (0, 0); pA = pO + dir(-40); pB = pO + dir(32); pC = pO + dir(176); draw(pA--pO--pB--pC--pA); draw(pO--pC); label("$O$", pO, 2 * E); label("$A$", pA, SE);
